data.name: webUrl.ToolTip
data.value:
The URL to the directory that contains all the version folders containing the patch files Example: http://www.awesome.com/Patches/
If the example URL existed, then when the patcher is checking for new patches, it would check the users current version, and for example, if the users current version were '0' then it would check "http://www.awesome.com/Patches/1/" for patches.

data.name: startVer.ToolTip
data.value: The version to use as the current version for users before they ever patch. (It is reccommended to change this and the WZ files that users get with your installer/server client download on a regular basis according to the latest patch version)
